    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is a pristine 1995 Acura NSX-T, an analog masterpiece in showroom condition. This example features the legendary C30A 3.0L V6 with VTEC, utilizing factory titanium connecting rods and an 8,000 RPM redline. The mid-engine layout remains perfectly balanced, with the five-speed manual transaxle offering crisp, short-throw engagement and optimal gear spacing. The all-aluminum monocoque chassis is structurally flawless, and the double-wishbone suspension components retain their factory-spec rigidity and bushings. This vehicle has undergone a comprehensive mechanical audit, confirming zero fluid seepage, peak compression across all cylinders, and a flawless undercarriage. Finished in a mirror-like Formula Red, this NSX represents a turn-key opportunity for an enthusiast seeking the pinnacle of 90s Japanese engineering.",
